reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Always read reviews….
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for my 22 month old for Christmas, and thought it would be a good sized mat and toy for her to play with based on the photo and description. When it arrived, the cars were significantly smaller (about the size of her hand), and the mat is so small that she can’t sit on it while playing with the cars (only a few roads on each side). Definitely a disappointment. I’m also concerned that the packaging notes this is for 3+, even though the description indicates it would be safer for younger children. Had I read the reviews before I purchased I would have seen similar comments. Next time I’ll remember to read reviews before purchasing.
